productReviews.reviewText: I saw one of these in New Zealand and I bought one.
My neighbor Lular has one of these. She works as a cake decorator and she says it looks ragged.
The box this comes in is 3 kilometer by 5 inch and weights 13 ton.
heard about this on hip-hop music radio, decided to give it a try.
one of my hobbies is theater. and when i'm acting this works great.
